s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會就去德國exchange下啦<br />\n去完兩三個月就識講同拎到語感架啦<br />\n不過都要睇彩數, 好多人去到識到既人都同佢地講返英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好撚好彩唔知點解身邊個個(外國人)都同我講德文, 一個月之後德文腦已洗, 從此識講"},{"pid":"959859b0ea52dffe1ee89fab6a093c7845e770c2","tid":382271,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌， 你搞到我好撚驚<br />\n我嚟咗台灣讀德文<br />\n11號就開學<br />\n我仲要係負碌先入到呢間學校<br />\n啲師兄話佢哋對成績要求都幾高<br />\n俾你咁樣嚇一嚇<br />\n我驚我真係gard唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會就去德國exchange下啦<br />\n去完兩三個月就識講同拎到語感架啦<br />\n不過都要睇彩數, 好多人去到識到既人都同佢地講返英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好撚好彩唔知點解身邊個個(外國人)都同我講德文, 一個月之後德文腦已洗, 從此識講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陰陽中都背撚死 點學"},{"pid":"2efba122f5e90bf5a0ba52c5ff1475fb569eb4aa","tid":382271,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌， 你搞到我好撚驚<br />\n我嚟咗台灣讀德文<br />\n11號就開學<br />\n我仲要係負碌先入到呢間學校<br />\n啲師兄話佢哋對成績要求都幾高<br />\n俾你咁樣嚇一嚇<br />\n我驚我真係gard唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會就去德國exchange下啦<br />\n去完兩三個月就識講同拎到語感架啦<br />\n不過都要睇彩數, 好多人去到識到既人都同佢地講返英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好撚好彩唔知點解身邊個個(外國人)都同我講德文, 一個月之後德文腦已洗, 從此識講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陰陽中都背撚死 點學</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你背英文字咪又係咁背, 將der/die/das融入去當spelling一齊背埋佢咪得<br />\n就算英文都有自己既麻煩嘢啦, 串法同讀音冇關, 要額外喺個腦用多個位記讀音<br />\n同埋記記下就發覺有啲general rules, 好多字唔需要再特登記gender"},{"pid":"06491a72bdc8e435bef88b34964ae4a7d20617ae","tid":382271,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇前面個prepositions，前面個verbs是否dativ verbs (helfen, danken, gefallen...), 是否指時間/地點/移動...<br />\n<br />\n不過都要靠語感去feel下邊d係direkt/indirekt object，錯得多都未必會識</blockquote><br />\nDirekt同indirekt objec如果自己寫我真係唔係好分到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2077a3cd8f302d262412eabf6760a41b890235e","tid":382271,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名跟進 我Take左德文Credit Course<br />\n聽日Yr1開Sem開始讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學german 1好濕碎 當我都A到個course你冇理由唔得"},{"pid":"339cffcbcfa510c0cd781bfa143153f8e5d9ed64","tid":382271,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打試下用Dictionary啦<br />\n<a href=\"http://Dict.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDict.cc&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1176d38c\" target=\"_blank\">http://Dict.cc</a>同<a href=\"http://Leo.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FLeo.org&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7e18b387\" target=\"_blank\">http://Leo.org</a>呢兩個都唔錯<br />\n查完就知個verb係跟Dativ定Akkusativ<br />\n用多啲就知要跟咩㗎喇<br />\n同埋網上都有好多表可以背<br />\n例如：<a href=\"http://mein-deutschbuch.de/dativ-und-akkusativ-ergaenzung.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmein-deutschbuch.de%2Fdativ-und-akkusativ-er